                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310908-340-off1750 t18310908-340-cd1751"></join>, 1 reticule, value 6d.; 1 handkerchief, value 1s.; 1 purse, value 1s.; 4 half-crowns, and 8 shillings, the property of 
                     
